com.opera.core.systems.mobile

Enum MobileDevices

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MobileDevices>
      • com.opera.core.systems.mobile.MobileDevices
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MobileDevices>

    public enum MobileDevices
extends Enum<MobileDevices>
    A convenience list of different mobile device's emulation settings for use with OperaSettings.emulate(MobileDevices). The list is kept in sync with the profile list in the omlauncher binary shipped alongside the Opera Mobile Emulator.
